latestPosts.caption:
Just a bunch of main characters on a 2000s core girls’ trip—sunburnt, unbothered, and borderline iconic.
BRB still dancing like aserejé ja de je 🏖️🎶💃

A girls trip straight out of a 2000s summer dream — messy buns, loud laughs, beach hair, and The Ketchup Song on full blast🦩

It felt like a scene from an old music video… low-effort fits, sandy feet, and zero worries. Just sun, sea, and serotonin.
Still not over how good it felt to just live, dance like no one’s watching (they were), and be completely unserious for a few days 💃🫶

Tag the girlies who’d still slay a girls trip like it’s 2003☀️✨

Concept/ direction/ edit: @gurleendahelay yours truly🥰
